No. 10-647. George Wysocki, Petitioner v. International Business Machines Corporation, dba IBM, Inc. 562 U.S. 1169, 131 S. Ct. 945,

178 L. Ed. 2d 804,

2011 U.S. LEXIS 54. January 10, 2011.

Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Sixth Circuit denied.

Justice Breyer took no part in the consideration or decision of this petition.

Same case below, 607 F.3d 1102.
